{"tid":2506160,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"啫啫滑雞煲（239336），我求下你唔好自殺。","createTime":"2021-04-27T06:37:00.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-27T07:30:18.000Z","uid":134071,"like":18,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"5351f5b4a5c9788829b99817d7236c1e59dc50a2","tid":2506160,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T06:37:00.000Z","msg":"我昨日寫錯料，己經向大家道歎。而家再次道歉。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但昨日引起既罵戰仲有餘波，啫啫滑雞煲（239336）話要自殺。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2506058/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2506058/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n件事攪成咁，我非常抱歉。<br />\n<br />\n但我好想講<br />\n1）件事100%錯在我身上，唔關你同其他人事。希望所有人停止罵戰。<br />\n2）你自殺，咪只係仇家高興。<strong>佢哋係完全唔會同情你。</strong>（李私煙死左，我地都會高與）<br />\n傷心既只有手足。<br />\n<br />\n我以前不斷比B612 星人狙擊，都諗過自殺<br />\n結果而家？B612 星人被ban, 我仲係連登。<br />\n<br />\n繼續支撐下去，生存下去，就係最好既報復。（適用於所有香港手足。）<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n（同埋我係原本個post既#305手快打錯字，非常抱歉。我希望任何人都唔好因為呢單野無左條命，包括啫啫滑雞煲你。）"},{"pid":"b600afb7a6ae2a3e99e4a5d8e0431acd3c3e02d5","tid":2506160,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T06:37:57.000Z","msg":"唔好自殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1f104a2e481d526db0bcac9f6c32e2268401ad8","tid":2506160,"uid":38904,"like":8,"dislike":6,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T06:38:17.000Z","msg":"我想條賤種快啲死喎<br />\n點解手足俾黑警搞死<br />\n但係佢可以風流快活上連登?"},{"pid":"0e30fff4aa11e6f6648caf749ee73ccbfd6ddd0e","tid":2506160,"uid":14103,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T06:40:18.000Z","msg":"拉拉拉 希望佢睇唔到"},{"pid":"8a24c2c9f8a379e0be799eb5118e5de6aefafc8d","tid":2506160,"uid":134071,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"e1f104a2e481d526db0bcac9f6c32e2268401ad8","tid":2506160,"uid":38904,"like":8,"dislike":6,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T06:38:17.000Z","msg":"我想條賤種快啲死喎<br />